{"tid":889953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"藍潔瑛：我想拍飛越瘋人院","createTime":"2018-11-05T02:52:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-05T18:58:22.000Z","uid":23058,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"88a6eefb79e9eaa50b5a9b2427471f3a92ea62b0","tid":889953,"uid":23058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T02:52:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-11-05/590/20181105000017.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-11-05%2F590%2F20181105000017.jpg&h=034c9303&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾被封為「靚絕五台山」的港星藍潔瑛，昨（3日）被發現暴斃家中，享年55歲，讓許多影迷和圈內好友惋惜，雖然她已淡出螢光幕前多年，但其實仍對演戲有熱情，好友受訪透露，藍潔瑛一直有想復出的意願，可惜最後還是沒了遺願。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據港媒《東方日報》報導，藍潔瑛的密友楊曼莉，透露兩人最近一次聯絡在一個月前，當時通電話時，藍潔瑛病得很重，咳嗽咳不停，連聲音都變了，但是思路是清晰的，原本楊曼莉想去探望藍潔瑛，但對方說不用，「可能因為她生病，不想見人啦！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n楊曼莉悼念藍潔瑛。（圖／翻攝自楊曼莉微博）<br />\n楊曼莉說，圈內一直有不少人想邀請藍潔瑛拍戲，藍潔瑛對於復出演藝圈也很有興趣，尤其想拍陸版的《飛越杜鵑窩》（港、陸譯《飛越瘋人院》），<br />\n<a href=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcS_FK47sO6mC8u9X157AKMxT6Bfc4XutgR5NPgU7T-f3NJygdse「她想告訴別人她沒有精神病，只是被害了。」\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%253AANd9GcS_FK47sO6mC8u9X157AKMxT6Bfc4XutgR5NPgU7T-f3NJygdse%E3%80%8C%E5%A5%B9%E6%83%B3%E5%91%8A%E8%A8%B4%E5%88%A5%E4%BA%BA%E5%A5%B9%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E%E7%97%85%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AA%E6%98%AF%E8%A2%AB%E5%AE%B3%E4%BA%86%E3%80%82%E3%80%8D&d=%2Be4rXsWWmp3uQC6wDi9rWSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=aaab9a91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcS_FK47sO6mC8u9X157AKMxT6Bfc4XutgR5NPgU7T-f3NJygdse「她想告訴別人她沒有精神病，只是被害了。」</a><br />\n<br />\n另外，楊曼莉3日下午也PO出一張和藍潔瑛的合照，感傷寫下：「藍姐，懷念與您一起唱歌、吃飯、逛街的日子。祈願天國沒有欺凌，一路走好。」<br />\n<br />\n(中時電子報)<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20181104002830-260404\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20181104002830-260404&d=%2Be4rXsWWmp3uQC6wDi9rWSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=9993d85b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20181104002830-260404</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcS_FK47sO6mC8u9X157AKMxT6Bfc4XutgR5NPgU7T-f3NJygdse\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%253AANd9GcS_FK47sO6mC8u9X157AKMxT6Bfc4XutgR5NPgU7T-f3NJygdse&h=c1b7e196&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6d47a7490318568b67561a073222d5b789c6dc08","tid":889953,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T18:58:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}